Run with Pycharm and Python 2.7
Once the environment is good, run should be fine

    sudo apt install python-pip
    pip install six
    pip install matplotlib
    pip install numpy
    sudo apt install python-tk
    pip install networkx==1.11
    pip install pyyaml
    pip install pp # Optional
    apt install cmake

    pip insall lomap

